ca.cgjennings.ui

Interface BrowserPanel.ViewProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BrowserPanel.DefaultViewProvider
    Enclosing class:
    BrowserPanel

    public static interface BrowserPanel.ViewProvider
    An interface that acts as an adapter between components that can display HTML content and a browser panel. The BrowserPanel will create a new ViewProvider when it is instantiated and use it obtain a page display component.
